# EWP-006 — TenantMembership

**Engine:** VS08 – License, Subscription & Tenant Management Engine

**Milestone:** VS08A – Tenant Foundation

**Capability Contract:** CC-006 – TenantMembership

**Status:** Approved for Implementation

---

# Objective

Implement the **TenantMembership** aggregate exactly as defined by the approved CAP architecture.

This work package establishes the relationship between Platform Users and Tenants while keeping identity separate from organizational participation.

---

# Inputs

Implementation shall comply with:

* ES-001 Database Standards
* ES-008 Architecture & Domain Modeling
* ES-009 Data Ownership & Persistence
* ES-010 Platform Naming & Namespace
* ADR-008-001 through ADR-008-016
* DDS-101A
* CC-006

---

